What you need to know:  Kenya, who are ranked third in Africa, were drawn in Pool ‘B’ alongside Rwanda, South Africa and MauritiusTheir male counterparts have landed in a tricky Pool ‘B’ that has Gambia who are ranked first in Africa, Zambia and South AfricaThe technical bench might field Makokha and Agala in the women’s side due to their experience and exposure at the Tokyo 2020 Olympics Games